-- Parasitic Tentacles are long, fleshy organisms that dangle from ceilings Inside Jabu-Jabu's Belly. There are three of them, each with a different color: Red, Green and Blue that correspond with three electric fields that block Link's progress in the dungeon. They are highly electric and can only attack, or be harmed, when they expose their slender portion, which can be damaged by the Boomerang. Once defeated, they decompose in addition to their corresponding barrier. 